title: Milwaukee Fire Department honors We Energies with Community Hero Award (We Energies)
text: ( Source : We Energies ) The Milwaukee Fire Department ( MFD ) honored We Energies at its Meritorious and Community Service Awards Ceremony last night. The annual ceremony celebrates courageous men and women of the MFD, Milwaukee Police
